@model GrcMvc.Models.DTOs.AssessmentStatisticsDto
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.Localization
@inject IHtmlLocalizer<SharedResource> L
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = L["Assessment_Statistics_Title"].Value;
    Layout = "_Layout";
}

<div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row mb-3">
        <div class="col">
            <h2><i class="bi bi-bar-chart"></i> @L["Assessment_Statistics_Title"]</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="col text-end">
            <a asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-secondary">
                <i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i> @L["BackToList"]
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    @if (TempData["Error"] != null)
    {
        <div class="alert alert-danger alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
            @TempData["Error"]
            <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close"></button>
        </div>
    }

    <!-- Key Metrics Cards -->
    <div class="row mb-4">
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="card text-white bg-primary mb-3">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">@L["Assessment_TotalAssessments"]</h5>
                    <p class="card-text display-4">@Model.TotalAssessments</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="card text-white bg-success mb-3">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">@L["Assessment_Completed"]</h5>
                    <p class="card-text display-4">@Model.CompletedAssessments</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="card text-white bg-warning mb-3">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">@L["Assessment_InProgress"]</h5>
                    <p class="card-text display-4">@Model.InProgressAssessments</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="card text-white bg-danger mb-3">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">@L["Assessment_Overdue"]</h5>
                    <p class="card-text display-4">@Model.OverdueAssessments</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mb-4">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="card h-100">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">@L["Assessment_AverageScoresAndCompletion"]</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="row text-center">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <h6>@L["Assessment_AverageScore"]</h6>
                            <div class="display-4 text-info">@Model.AverageScore.ToString("F1")%</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <h6>@L["Assessment_CompletionRate"]</h6>
                            <div class="display-4 text-success">@Model.CompletionRate.ToString("F1")%</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="card h-100">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">@L["Assessment_PendingAssessments"]</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                    <div class="display-4 text-secondary">@Model.PendingAssessments</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Charts -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">@L["Assessment_AssessmentsByType"]</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <canvas id="typeChart"></canvas>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">@L["Assessment_StatusDistribution"]</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <canvas id="statusChart"></canvas>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

@section Scripts {
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
    <script>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            // Type Chart
            var typeCtx = document.getElementById('typeChart').getContext('2d');
            var typeData = @Html.Raw(Json.Serialize(Model.AssessmentsByType));

            new Chart(typeCtx, {
                type: 'pie',
                data: {
                    labels: Object.keys(typeData),
                    datasets: [{
                        data: Object.values(typeData),
                        backgroundColor: [
                            '#4e73df', '#1cc88a', '#36b9cc', '#f6c23e', '#e74a3b'
                        ]
                    }]
                }
            });

            // Status Chart
            var statusCtx = document.getElementById('statusChart').getContext('2d');
            var statusData = @Html.Raw(Json.Serialize(Model.StatusDistribution));

            new Chart(statusCtx, {
                type: 'doughnut',
                data: {
                    labels: Object.keys(statusData),
                    datasets: [{
                        data: Object.values(statusData),
                        backgroundColor: [
                            '#4e73df', '#1cc88a', '#36b9cc', '#f6c23e', '#e74a3b'
                        ]
                    }]
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
}
